    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《在虚拟现实僵尸末日中生存:僵尸病毒》是一款设定在首尔哈平站（弘大）的沉浸式虚拟现实僵尸生存射击游戏。 采用统一设计并针对元任务进行了优化，它提供了流畅的80帧每秒性能，通过轻量级资产和对焦渲染来最小化晕动症。 霓虹灯闪烁的街道、地铁隧道和废弃的俱乐部以真实的韩国细节被重现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/e53df97a1e3d462436edea1497f74bfb.poster.avif?t=1767063461\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/e53df97a1e3d462436edea1497f74bfb.webm?t=1767063461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/e53df97a1e3d462436edea1497f74bfb.mp4?t=1767063461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与缓慢且可预测的敌人不同，你将面对快速而聪明的韩国僵尸，它们会追击、侧翼并协调群组人工智能。 他们的行为会根据你的位置、噪音和视力进行调整，始终保持生存紧张。 配备超过20种逼真的武器，包括犬式步枪和犬式手枪，这些武器设计有手动装弹、双手操作、后坐力和真实的弹道学效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/bdef8da49888b5696d782aa9d85c34da.poster.avif?t=1767063461\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/bdef8da49888b5696d782aa9d85c34da.webm?t=1767063461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/bdef8da49888b5696d782aa9d85c34da.mp4?t=1767063461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《僵尸病毒》还强调了虚拟现实互动性:抓取武器、开门、移动物体，并触发动态反应，如可破坏物品、照明和声音。 这款游戏采用模块化设计和多人就绪架构，使用光子/融合技术为未来打造。 期待定期更新新的地图、武器和僵尸类型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关键特点:韩国背景 – 以真实感探索哈平（弘大）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速智能僵尸——更聪明、更快捷、更危险的人工智能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20多种逼真武器 – 包括标志性的警犬和警犬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式虚拟现实战斗 – 手动重新装填、后坐力、近战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种模式 – 战役、生存、无尽大军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时更新 – 持续的新内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/bb225a12226c2d1a9148864f951488d5.poster.avif?t=1767063461\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/bb225a12226c2d1a9148864f951488d5.webm?t=1767063461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222270/extras/bb225a12226c2d1a9148864f951488d5.mp4?t=1767063461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
